uct_id":100001901,"comment_content":"再优秀的人都要认识自己的不足，予以弥补。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":44855,"user_name":"caohuan","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1256428,"ip_address":"","ucode":"4B092E33F3DF1E","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/2b/ec/af6d0b10.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1543500447,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1543500447","product_id":100001901,"comment_content":"学术界 与 工业界 不一样，学术界 有点眼高手低，技术前瞻性很强，工业界 动手能力很强，商业化能力较强，一旦成功 回报多多。","like_count":0}]}